# Quick Reply Generator

## Description
A skill that generates short, polite, and confident replies to given messages. The skill creates professional yet friendly responses that are under 3 lines with no explanations, ready to send as-is.

## Trigger Conditions
- Automatically activates when user requests help with crafting replies
- Responds to phrases like "generate reply", "create response", "reply to this", "help me respond"
- Available when user submits a message that needs a response

## Functionality
- Generates short replies (under 3 lines)
- Maintains professional but friendly tone
- Creates polite and confident responses
- Adds no unnecessary explanations
- Preserves the intent of addressing the original message
- Outputs ready-to-send replies

## Usage Examples
- "Help me reply to this message"
- "Generate a response to this"
- "Create a polite reply"
- "Reply to: [message text]"
- "How should I respond to this?"

## Parameters
- Input: Original message that needs a response
- Output: Short, polite, confident reply ready to send

## Constraints
- Reply must be under 3 lines
- Tone must be professional but friendly
- No explanations or additional commentary
- Response should address the original message appropriately
- Concise and to the point
